      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775848786822,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 42.75985839396356,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Security Flow:\n\n1. Client sends GET request with x-api-key header\n2. API Gateway forwards request to Lambda\n3. Lambda extracts x-api-key from headers\n4. Lambda calls KMS to decrypt API_SECRET_KEY environment variable\n5. Lambda compares received key with decrypted expected key\n6. If valid: Generate secure passcode using secrets.choice()\n7. Return JSON response with passcode and metadata\n\nKMS Benefits:\n• Environment variables encrypted at rest\n• Only Lambda with proper IAM can decrypt\n• Cached decryption for performance\n• No plaintext secrets visible in AWS Console",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Security Flow:\n\n1. Client sends GET request with x-api-key header\n2. API Gateway forwards request to Lambda\n3. Lambda extracts x-api-key from headers\n4. Lambda calls KMS to decrypt API_SECRET_KEY environment variable\n5. Lambda compares received key with decrypted expected key\n6. If valid: Generate secure passcode using secrets.choice()\n7. Return JSON response with passcode and metadata\n\nKMS Benefits:\n• Environment variables encrypted at rest\n• Only Lambda with proper IAM can decrypt\n• Cached decryption for performance\n• No plaintext secrets visible in AWS Console",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 194,
      "index": "b0A",
      "autoResize": false
    },
